<br>
IMO, I'd say 16 - the age most start working, is the age they are fully accountable for their actions.  It's this age when they start contributing to society, generally.<br>
<br>
For those NOT of an age to be tried as an adult - I'd say the parent/guardian should be help responsible for the actions of the child.  I bet THAT would force some parenting changes on people. . . . <p></br>

